Must have
More than 1 year of experience as a Back-end developer;
Hands-on experience working with Node.js, JavaScript and TypeScript
Knowledge and experience in NoSQL (e.g. MongoDB);
Server experience - Solving server and database logic issues;
Ability to work with MySQL;
Familiar with the Git version control system with GitHub/Gitlab;
Collaborate with Front-end developers to integrate user-facing elements with server-side logic;
Be able to read and translate English documents;
Good at research skills, teamwork skills, English basics.
Nice to have
Preferably experience in front-end development: React JS, Next JS framework;
Working experience with Docker, CRM System;
Experience with Cloud Service (AWS,Azure,Google Cloud);
Knowledge of Agile project management tools, e.g. JIRA;
Upgrade, maintain, and Fix Server-Side Errors.
Other
Sense of responsibility, self-motivation, independence, and critical thinking;
Provide training, help, and support to other team members;
Willingness to learn and build a deep understanding;
Be able to work independently and work in a team environment;
A passion for software development, new trends, and technologies in IT.
