Lưu tin
Chi tiết tin tuyển dụng
Mô tả công việc
Plan and execute SEO strategies (on-page and off-page) in conjunction with company’s overall goals and objectives;
Optimize content for better website’s conversion rates and user experience;
Plan and implement advertising activities on digital channels (Google Ads, LinkedIn Ads...);
Closely monitor the metrics, evaluate the effectiveness and optimize the budget;
Research user behavior on digital platforms, provide insights about customer personas for other teams;
Develop and expand access on other digital platforms;
Analyze the market, competitors and implement new customer acquisition and retention methods.
Yêu cầu ứng viên
Strong attention to detail with an analytical mind and outstanding problem-solving skills;
At least 2 years of digital marketing experience;
Proven experience and success across content marketing, SEO, PPC;
Ability to utilize marketing automation technology;
Experience in B2B technology industry is a plus;
Experience in working with global market is a plus;
Have knowledge of HTML, CSS is a plus;
Strong project management skills;
Ability to troubleshoot issues in a fast-paced environment;
Great time management, interpersonal and communication skills;
Good command of English (especially reading and writing).
Quyền lợi
Basic salary upto 20,000,000VND + allowance
Competitive 13th-month salary package
Review salary per 6 months of employment
Dynamic, flexible, and equal working environment
Working with a team full of young and passionate talents
