Chi tiết tin tuyển dụng
Mô tả công việc
Lead full-cycle data processing and management processes: inputting, updating, and maintaining data into databases with accuracy and completeness of information;
Ensure data quality assurance: review data for deficiencies or errors, correct any identifying and correcting errors or inconsistencies in data;
Conduct data analysis: Basic data analysis to generate reports or summaries, and extract meaningful insights from data sets;
Proactively work with the Data Services Leader to solve any issue or problem that might occur during the process that may impact the project;
Work closely with teammates and AI engineers to assess the feasibility and possible solutions to ensure progress and quality of data delivered.
Yêu cầu ứng viên
[Must have]
Fresh graduate or no experience but willing to learn and develop a career in data or IT;
Good communication skills (verbal and written) in both English and Vietnamese; Intermediate English (B1) and Chinese (HSK4);
Proactiveness, detailed-oriented, constant-learning mindset, good time management;
Strong interest in data and analytics projects and Artificial Intelligence technologies;
Proficient in Excel formulas, data structures, and basic visualization;
Experience of using with MS Office, PDF tools, and data tools;
Ability to research for other data tools as project needs;
Experience with data management flow and data storage;
Academic knowledge, work exposure, or interest in Data Analytics.
[Nice to have]
Personal laptop;
Previous experience is optional;
Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science or related technical fields;
Exposure to the AI or IT field.
Fluent in Japanese.
Quyền lợi
Compensation and Recognition:
Performance growth with full training will be provided;
Outstanding compensation package based on impact and contribution;
13th-month salary;
Unique growth and performance evaluation once a year.
Work-life balance and Well-being:
Flexible working time and remote work policy due to living location;
Personal healthcare insurance package;
Annual medical checkup;
Other company support for hospitalization, weddings, funerals, and offspring delivery.
Family support:
Children’s month budget allocated for employees (up to 18 years old).
Team and Culture:
Annual company trips and fun events throughout the year;
Monthly team bonding activities budget.
